    <div class="item featured-testimonial">
      <h1 class="chalet">Sola has given me the opportunity to be a creative stylist and an entrepreneur. Coming from a big salon and a chair rental environment, this is a definite step up. I have confidence, freedom and excitement every day coming to my studio. I love that I have my own space, but still have a community of other beauty professionals in the building.</h1>
      <h4>Samantha McCallum, Sola Oakville</h4>
    </div>

    <div class="item featured-testimonial">
      <h1 class="chalet">Sola has given me the opportunity to create the environment I was seeking but unable to financially do on a large scale. This is a game changer for Canadian’s. The support, encouragement and positive energy at Sola has revived my passion for my industry.</h1>
      <h4>Angela Hutchison, Sola Oakville</h4>
    </div>

    <div class="item featured-testimonial">
